import React, { Fragment } from "react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
/// Compoents
import PageTitle from "../../layouts/PageTitle";

/// Image
import img1 from "../../../images/card/1.png";
import img2 from "../../../images/card/2.png";
import img3 from "../../../images/card/3.png";
/// Bootstrap
import { Row, Card, Col, Button, Nav } from "react-bootstrap";

const UiCards = () => {
  return (
    <Fragment>
      <PageTitle activeMenu="Card" pageContent="Card" motherMenu="Bootstrap" />
      <Row>
        <Col xl="3" sm="6">
          <Card className="bg-secondary text-white">
            <Card.Header>
              <Card.Title className="text-white">
                Secondary card title
              </Card.Title>
            </Card.Header>
            <Card.Body className=" mb-0">
              <Card.Text>
            
              </Card.Text>
              <Button
                as="a"
                variant=" "
                href="#"
                className="btn-card text-secondary mt-3 bg-white"
              >
                Go somewhere
              </Button>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer className=" border-0 bg-transparent text-white">
              Last updateed 3 min ago
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col xl="3" sm="6">
          <Card className="bg-success text-white">
            <Card.Header>
              <Card.Title className="text-white">Success card title</Card.Title>
            </Card.Header>
            <Card.Body className=" mb-0">
              <Card.Text>
            
              </Card.Text>
              <Button
                as="a"
                variant=" "
                href="#"
                className="btn-card text-success mt-3 bg-white"
              >
                Go somewhere
              </Button>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer className=" border-0 bg-transparent text-white">
              Last updateed 3 min ago
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col xl="3" sm="6">
          <Card className="bg-danger text-white">
            <Card.Header>
              <Card.Title className="text-white">Danger card title</Card.Title>
            </Card.Header>
            <Card.Body className=" mb-0">
              <Card.Text>
                Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up
                the bulk of the card's content.
              </Card.Text>
              <Button
                as="a"
                variant="danger light"
                href="#"
                className="btn-card text-danger mt-3 bg-white"
              >
                Go somewhere
              </Button>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer className=" border-0 bg-transparent text-white">
              Last updateed 3 min ago
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col xl="3" sm="6">
          <Card className="bg-warning text-white">
            <Card.Header>
              <Card.Title className="text-white">Warning card title</Card.Title>
            </Card.Header>
            <Card.Body className=" mb-0">
              <Card.Text>
                Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up
                the bulk of the card's content.
              </Card.Text>
              <Button
                as="a"
                variant="warning light"
                href="#"
                className="btn-card tet-warning mt-3 bg-white"
              >
                Go somewhere
              </Button>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer className=" border-0 bg-transparent text-white">
              Last updateed 3 min ago
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
        </Col>
       
       
      
        
       
      </Row>
    </Fragment>
  );
};

export default UiCards;
